<h1>
            Commands
        </h1>
        <ul>
            <li>
                When you are joined in, you can use commands to interact with the game
            </li>
            <li>
                Type <i>/list</i> in chat to get the list of commands and <i>/help</i> to get help about one
            </li>
            <li>
                Commands are powerful, you can change the board size, kick another player or consult statistics
            </li>
            <li>
                Some important commands require to be a <i>super user</i>, please do not abuse of theses commands
            </li>
        </ul>